    "summary": "This section, titled \"数据描述\" (Data Description) on page 27, provides a quantitative overview of market financial performance from 2021 to 2025. It covers two primary topics: annual market revenue scale and year-over-year growth rates. The content is visualized using a bar chart for revenue metrics (unit: 亿元) and a line chart for growth rate percentages. Specific dates and values include annual revenues of 364.8 (2021), 350.8 (2022), 347.2 (2023), 361.0 (2024), and 364.6 (2025), alongside YoY growth rates of -3.82% (2021–2022), -1.05% (2022–2023), 3.98% (2023–2024), and 0.99% (2024–2025). Key claims indicate a temporary market revenue decline from 2021 to 2023, followed by a recovery and projected growth through 2025, corresponding to a shift from negative to positive annual growth. The section relies on quantitative, time-series financial evidence presented through charts. It does not contain definitions, procedures, tabular data, or specific named entities beyond the implied market context."
