    "summary": "This section provides a quantitative trend analysis of market revenue and year-over-year growth rates from 2021 to 2025. It supports retrieval for questions regarding:\n- **Topics & Claims:** Market revenue trajectory, specifically identifying a contraction phase (2021–2023) followed by a recovery and expansion phase (2024–2025).\n- **Dates & Timeframes:** Annual intervals spanning 2021 through 2025.\n- **Metrics & Entities:** Market revenue scale (in billions of RMB) and year-over-year growth rates (in percentages).\n- **Specific Data Points:** Exact revenue figures (364.8B in 2021, 350.8B in 2022, 347.2B in 2023, 361.0B in 2024, 364.6B in 2025) and corresponding growth rates (-3.82% for 2021–2022, -1.05% for 2022–2023, +3.98% for 2023–2024, +0.99% for 2024–2025).\n- **Evidence Types:** Historical and projected quantitative financial metrics.\nThe section directly answers queries about annual market size, growth rate fluctuations, performance inflection points, and specific numerical benchmarks for the five-year period."
