  {
    "node_id": "0093",
    "title": "图例",
    "page_range": "27",
    "summary": "This section provides chart legends and descriptive metadata for visualizations analyzing the Hong Kong, Macao, and Taiwan mobile game market. It enables retrieval for questions regarding:\n- **Topics & Entities:** Mobile game market revenue scale, growth trends, and revenue concentration in the Hong Kong, Macao, and Taiwan regions.\n- **Dates:** 2023, 2024, and 2025.\n- **Definitions & Visual Encoding:** Blue bars represent revenue scale (in 100 million RMB); cyan-green lines represent growth rate (%); segmented colors denote revenue share by game ranking tier (blue: ranks 1–10, cyan: 11–50, green: 51–200, orange: others).\n- **Metrics:** Revenue scale (亿元/人民币), year-over-year growth rate (%), and market revenue concentration/proportion by ranking bracket.\n- **Figures & Tables:** Describes a combined bar/line chart tracking revenue and growth, and a segmented bar chart illustrating market concentration. Notes that a detailed data table follows (\"具体数据如下：\").\n- **Evidence & Source:** Data is independently researched and produced by 点点数据 (Diandian Data).\n- **Procedures & Claims:** None explicitly stated; the section is purely descriptive and legend-focused.\n- **Retrieval Use Cases:** Answers questions on how to interpret the provided market charts, what timeframes and regions are analyzed, how revenue is distributed across top-performing vs. mid/low-tier games, the specific units used for financial and growth metrics, and the origin of the market data."
