    "summary": "This section provides quantitative market data for 2025, answering questions regarding the revenue distribution of mobile games by ranking tier. \n- **Date:** 2025\n- **Topics/Entities:** Mobile game revenue concentration categorized by rank (Top 1–10, 11–50, 51–200, and Others)\n- **Metrics:** Revenue share percentages per tier: 1–10 (23.24%), 11–50 (28.34%), 51–200 (25.37%), Others (23.05%)\n- **Evidence Type:** Quantitative statistical data\n- **Answerable Questions:** What was the 2025 revenue share breakdown for mobile games across the top 10, 11–50, 51–200, and other ranking tiers? How is mobile game revenue distributed by rank in 2025?\nThe section contains no definitions, procedures, qualitative claims, tables, or figures, focusing exclusively on numerical revenue distribution metrics."
